data.description: This well maintained property is ready for anything. Horse pasture at the bottom of the property with its own gate. Pasture is roughly 1/4 acre. Tree spacing throughout the property. Recent updates inside and outside make this property very welcoming for a new owner. Bring your dreams, ideas, tools, and toys because it can all fit on this 2 acre property. Property is beautifully tiered to support multiple ventures. Community has a lake, bbq, and picnic area. Near Swansboro Airport and Mosquito fire district.
